text: I'm heartbroken by the fatal and senseless shooting in Parkland, Florida this afternoon.  My thoughts are with all of the victims, their families, and the first responders in the aftermath of this tragedy.

I am on board the train involved in the crash, and am safe.  Appreciate all who have reached out and incredibly grateful for the first responders.  Please join me in praying for those receiving medical care & their families.
Praying for my good friend @SteveScalise & all affected. As always, incredibly grateful for the service and bravery of @CapitolPolice
Tonight the House passed bipartisan legislation that I intro'd with @KathleenRice to streamline employee access at airports nationwide.
I'll be on with @BrentAxeMedia at 5:05 p.m. to talk about bipartisan legislation to reform the NCAA
I'll be on with @JoeWAUB @FLNewsRadio at 8:38 to discuss the start of the new Congress #NY24
